title: Jimi Hendrix, Lifelines - The LA Forum Concert - April 26, 1969
description:
Jimi Hendrix
LIFELINES - The Jimi Hendrix Story, CD IV - The L.A. Forum Concert (1990)

1969-04-26, Los Angeles Forum, Inglewood, Los Angeles, CA

Sound quality is great. This official CD contains (contrary to many bootlegs) the complete versions of Spanish Castle Magic and the Star Spangled Banner, but Tax Free is not complete. Low vocals in later part of Voodoo Child (Slight Return).

Tracks:
1. Tax Free (incomplete)
2. Red House
3. Spanish Castle Magic
4. Star Spangled Banner
5. Purple Haze
6. I Don&#039;t Live Today
7. Voodoo Child (Slight Return) / Sunshine Of Your Love

Foxy Lady is missing (in between Tax Free and Red House)
